        "content": "## 🗺️ Distribución de UEs\n\n| UE | gNB | IMSI | Slice | Resultado |\n|----|-----|------|-------|-----------|\n| srsue_5g | srsgnb | 895 | SD=000001 | ✅ 192.168.100.x |\n| nr_ue | gNB1 | 896 | SD=000001 | ✅ 192.168.100.x |\n| nr_ue2 | gNB2 | 898 | SD=000001 | ✅ 192.168.100.x |\n| nr_ue3 | gNB2 | 899 | **SD=000002** | ✅ **192.168.200.x** |\n| nr_ue_bad_supi | gNB1 | 905 | SD=000001 | ❌ Unknown Subscriber |\n| nr_ue_bad_ki | gNB1 | 906 | SD=000001 | ❌ Auth Failure |\n| nr_ue_bad_dnn | gNB1 | 908 | SD=000001 | ⚠️ Reg OK / PDU ❌ |\n| nr_ue_bad_sst | gNB2 | 909 | SD=**000003** | ❌ NSSAI not found |",
